query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-videoview',
'archive',
'audio-streaming',
'avr',
'backtracking',
'directive',
'ejabberd',
'h2o',
'icalendar',
'log4net',
'na',
'ncurses',
'pydev',
'raspbian',
'symfony4');
